Chinese President Xi Jinping on Tuesday stressed attentive, enthusiastic and targeted services for retired cadres, urging those working in the field to strive for remarkable accomplishments in their ordinary positions. Xi, also general secretary of the Communist Party of China Central Committee and chairman of the Central Military Commission, made the remarks in an instruction to a national commendation meeting on work related to retired cadres. (Cover: Medical staff provide vaccination service for retired cadres in Nanjing, China's Jiangsu Province, Oct. 27, 2021. /CFP)